\c 95
\s Jehovha ngaakudzwe ateererwe navanhu
\p
\v 1 Uyai, tiimbire Jehovha; Ngatipururudzei dombo rokuponeswa kwedu.
\v 2 Ngatisvike pamberi pake tichivonga, Ngatimupururudzei namapisarema,
\v 3 Nokuti Jehovha ndiMwari mukuru, ,Mambo mukuru anokunda vamwari vose.
\v 4 Nzvimbo dzakadzika dzapasi dziri muruoko rwake; Misoro yamakomo ndeyakewo.
\v 5 Gungwa nderake, ndiye akariita; Maoko ake akaumba nyika yakaoma.
\v 6 Uyai, tinamate tikotamire pasi; Ngatipfugame pamberi paJehovha Muiti wedu.
\v 7 Nokuti ndiye Mwari wedu, Isu tiri vanhu vanofudzwa naye, namakwai oruoko rwake. Nhasi dai muchinzwa henyu izwi rake!
\v 8 Regai kuomesa mwoyo yenyu sapaMeribha, Sapazuva reMasa murenje;
\v 9 Panguva yandakaidzwa namadzibaba enyu, Vakandiidza, vakaona zvandakaita.
\v 10 Ndakanza ndine shune iatuusqt:+ porudzi urwo makore makumi mana, Ndikati, `Ndivanhu vakarashika pamwoyo yavo, Havana kuziva nzira dzangu;'
\v 11 Saka ndakapika pakutsamwa kwangu, ndikati,Havangazopindi pazororo rangu.' "
